try making a server and not useing the default one that comes with moparscape. go to download section and find testscape open that up start it then go to moparscape don’t press start server just log in the local host (the numbers that are there when u start) then your on your server. for further info use the how to make a server tut in the tutorial section OR go into the server advitisement section and find an ip address witch u can log into
